snippet.title: Marvel Heroes Omega Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Marvel Heroes Omega assembles one of the largest gatherings of iconic Super Heroes, Super Villains, and locations from the Marvel Universe for PlayStation®4 and Xbox One®. Band together with fellow adventurers, take the fight to Doctor Doom in an epic nine-chapter story campaign, and experience your favorite heroes, including Captain America, Daredevil, Spider-Man, Wolverine, Captain Marvel, and more!

Download now from the PlayStation and Xbox Stores now FOR FREE! 

https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/marvel-heroes-omega-ps4/
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/marvel-heroes-omega/bsgzg16lm67p
https://marvelheroes.com/
